description: GemBox.Spreadsheet is a .NET component that enables developers to read, write, convert and print spreadsheet files (XLSX, XLS, ODS, CSV, HTML, PDF or XPS) from their .NET applications using one simple API.
releaseNotes:
- Fixed issue with reading pivot table worksheet source.
- Fixed issue with custom number format ('mmm').
- Fixed issue with formatting large number of cells.
- Fixed issue with copying worksheet that has large range of merged cells.
- Fixed issue with exporting DataGridViewImageCell that has ImageLayout set to Normal.
- Improved CellRange.Clear() method's performance.
- Fixed issue when writing cell value of type Int64/UInt64 to XLSX file.
- Fixed issue when setting cell value of float type.
- Added reading of hyperlink's default formatting in HTML.
summary: GemBox.Spreadsheet is a .NET component for reading and writing spreadsheet files (XLSX, XLS, CSV, ODS, HTML, PDF and XPS).
